snippet.title: Grace Liu - Get In My Car (Official Video)

localized.description:
Written by Patrice Wilson, Yanchun Liu and Tom Chou. Produced by Patrice Wilson and Tom Chou. Mixed and mastered by Heath Ripplinger. Video directed by Ian Hotchkiss and Chris Lowe. Executive Producer Patrice Wilson. Music composed by Jaklo. Get it it now on ITunes:   https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/get-in-my-car-single/id839173272 

Subscribe Grace's Youtube channel: http://www.youtube.com/user/GraceLiuMusic
Follow me on Twitter: https://twitter.com/GraceLiuMusic
Let It Go cover MV: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T0EGjKCFJrw

Get In My Car Lyrics:
Verses:
Open(or let down) the moon-roof(or sunroof or window), comes the sound of twittering(or chirping),
My heart is fluttering, like a swallow flapping its wings.
Flying over the rainbow, smooching the clouds for fun,
Side by side( or cheek by jowl), we are soaring towards the sun.

Chorus
Get in my car so we can fly away, up to the sky
Get in my car so we can fly away, high above the rainbow 
my car goes chichy chichy bang bang, chichy chichy bang bang
fly up in the sky, chichy chichy bang bang, chichy chichy bang bang Fly all over the world.

Rap:
wǒ tiān shàng fēi～fēi
wǎng gāo chǔ zhuī～zhuī
wǒ kàn jiàn cǎi hóng
wǒ chuān yuè cháng chéng
bù tíng de chōng～chōng
huá guò tiān kōng～kōng
gēn zhù shì jiè yī qǐ bù tíng de zhuǎn dòng (Come On Now)
tiào shàng lái，zuò wǒ chē，wǒ mén yī qǐ qù pài duì
kuài kuài dǎ kāi tiān chuāng，ràng shǒu bù tíng de wǎng shàng huī
wǒ kuài yào rěn bù zhù，nǐ zhè shēn yī fú de tài dù
nǐ dǒng wǒ fēng dù，jiù xiàng wàn néng chē fēi tiān de sù dù
